name: Super High IQ Maze Game - Beta
name_original: Super High IQ Maze Game - Beta
description:
if you can solve this maze puzzle game, then you have a super high IQ, but if you can't and get stuck, then you have a low IQ...sorry.

How to play:

Press the LEFT and RIGHT ARROW Keys to rotate map and guide the ball through the maze

Press R to reset the map if you are stupid
